7
00:00:50,717 --> 00:00:51,760
<font color="japanese">人事部？

8
00:00:51,843 --> 00:00:53,344
<font color="japanese">何か申請を？

9
00:00:54,262 --> 00:00:55,096
<font color="japanese">いや

10
00:00:57,682 --> 00:00:59,976
<font color="japanese">人事部から…

11
